description:
'Dune: Part Two' (2024) is an upcoming American film directed by Denis Villeneuve. It will be released to the general audience on March 1, 2024.

This market will resolve to ”'Yes” if, when checked on the resolution date, 'Dune: Part Two' has a 90% or higher Tomatometer rating at Rotten Tomatoes. Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”. 

The resolution source (Tomatometer All Critics Score rating at Rotten Tomatoes' movie profile: https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dune_part_two) for this market will be checked on the resolution date - March 4, 2024 at 12:00 PM ET.

---------------

Rotten Tomatoes' Tomatometer is the percentage of all Approved Tomatometer Critics who have given this movie a positive review.

If for any reason the resolution data is unavailable, the resolution source will be checked every hour until the actual data is available. If the data is not available on the resolution source by March 11, 2024 at 12:00 PM ET, this market will resolve to 50/50.
